@META
dir: src/components/ui
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 20
stack: React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion

@EXPORTS
index.ts: Box|Stack|Grid|Button|GlassSurface|GreySurface|ElectricBorder|Lightning|LightningBackground|LaserFlow|ProfileCard|DecryptedText|FallingText|FuzzyText|FluidGlass|FluidGlassSimple|StatCard|SectionHeader — barrel export of all UI components
button.tsx: Button — polymorphic button with variants (primary|secondary|ghost|outline|danger) & sizes
box.tsx: Box — generic container with padding/margin/bg props
stack.tsx: Stack — flex column/row layout with gap
grid.tsx: Grid — CSS grid layout with responsive columns
glass-surface.tsx: GlassSurface — glassmorphism card with backdrop blur
grey-surface.tsx: GreySurface — muted surface variant
fluid-glass.tsx: FluidGlass — animated glass effect (desktop only, performance-gated)
fluid-glass-simple.tsx: FluidGlassSimple — lightweight glass fallback for mobile
fluid-glass-fallback.tsx: FluidGlassFallback — static fallback for low-perf devices
electric-border.tsx: ElectricBorder — animated electric glow border effect
lightning.tsx: Lightning — SVG lightning bolt effect
lightning-background.tsx: LightningBackground — full-page lightning background
laser-flow.tsx: LaserFlow — animated laser line effect
profile-card.tsx: ProfileCard — user profile display card
decrypted-text.tsx: DecryptedText — text reveal animation (typing effect)
falling-text.tsx: FallingText — physics-based falling text animation
fuzzy-text.tsx: FuzzyText — glitch/fuzzy text effect
stat-card.tsx: StatCard — gamification stat display (XP, level, streak)
section-header.tsx: SectionHeader — page section header with gradient text
button.stories.tsx: ButtonStories — Storybook stories for Button

@INTERFACES
ButtonProps: { variant:enum, size:enum, asChild?:boolean } & HTML button attrs
BoxProps: { as?:ElementType, p?:string, m?:string, bg?:string, className?:string }
StackProps: { direction?:"row"|"col", gap?:string, align?:string, justify?:string }
GridProps: { cols?:number|{sm,md,lg}, gap?:string }

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: @/lib/utils (cn), @/lib/theme, @/hooks/use-performance-check, @/hooks/use-reduced-motion
external: react, framer-motion, lucide-react, @radix-ui/react-slot, clsx, tailwind-merge, matter-js (FallingText physics)

@STANDARDS
- All components use cn() for Tailwind class merging
- Glass effects gated by usePerformanceCheck — fallback on mobile/low-end
- Button uses Radix Slot for polymorphic "asChild" pattern
- Dark theme by default (gray-900 backgrounds, white text)
- Design tokens from src/lib/theme.ts

@WARNINGS
- FluidGlass uses WebGL/canvas — heavy on GPU, only rendered on desktop with 4+ cores
- FallingText depends on matter-js physics engine — large dependency for text effect
- Some components have Storybook stories (*.stories.tsx)
